Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉佳子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.26,0:00:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你曾經是個男的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又要說那種話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來聽我說到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是為了真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須要變回男人才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我相似的雌雄同株
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像倒泡炒麵的水失敗了  把麵全灑到了池子裡的一副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易集齊的積分卡準備去用掉的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果發現過期了以後的表情…這樣才對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你還有回敬玩笑的心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫！  真由氏對你非常失望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝傻可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把小琉佳給弄哭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼你會知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請她一起來實驗室  結果突然就哭起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我問她怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說被你說自己是男的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-Mail的事情也聽說了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-Mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想矇混過關可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫應該好好向小琉佳道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然對漆原小姐說那麼過分的話？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  等等  不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這其中有很深的原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼原因？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助手  跟我來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  下一封要消除的D-Mail
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是發給琉佳子出生之前的他母親的呼叫器的簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漆原小姐其實是男的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…男的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說跟橋田一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  樣子看上去是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還可以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  要拯救真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不得不讓琉佳子變回男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這次岡部知道漆原小姐發送的D-Mail的內容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不用特意跟她說明事實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞞著她自己解決不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道琉佳子母親的呼叫器號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說  比起低劣的小動作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他真相才是有誠意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那誠意的結果就是讓她哭了不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你平常的「設定」對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玩笑對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒想過岡部師傅會說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是立了flag嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,flag？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:05:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒說什麼「這場戰鬥結束後就會結婚」之類的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是死亡flag
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的是戀愛flag
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  被最喜歡的岡部說「你是個男的」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女心都碎了一地了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…但是  琉佳子是男的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是前一個世界線上的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有重要的話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能到神社來一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我才是  哭了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後？  你說有重要的話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信岡部師傅說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是讓我變回男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我成為戀人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀…戀人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要當你的戀人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡岡部師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…明天  一天就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我成為戀人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…但是  你是男…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  你別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  明天一天就行的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就當你的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才稍微有點心動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以明天你要和漆原小姐去約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘋狂的科學家要和女高中生約會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:07:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說才這樣強忍羞恥和你這個助手商量怎樣才能約好會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說我不是助手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵喵  凶真要和誰出去約會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了  冰咖啡喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會對象是真由氏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說是這位呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這傢伙是助手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是為了修得奧義的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是隨心所欲地對身邊的各個女孩出手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  對身邊各種女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要說完讓人誤解的話就閃人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…  岡部你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了修得奧義就會什麼事都幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我說的是…  那個「設定」裡面的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連你也搬出「設定」來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說說而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:08:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有心上人  只要為了修得奧義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就什麼事都幹得出來的「設定」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼特別的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要生氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說  你要是這種設定的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和漆原小姐去約會不就行了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說一開始我就說了要去約會的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的話也讓我好好聽聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是約會的事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給已經和幾十個女孩子親熱過的我來處理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈  小栞  穗香  凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是遊戲中的女性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的是現實中的約會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:47.33,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：均為地名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說約會就是去青山或者表參道或者西麻布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流行時髦的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個豪華的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別的晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…這是另外一個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實中不存在的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都否定了還怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說  和艾薩克·牛頓一樣天生IQ170的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳凰院凶真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說感興趣的  比起女人來還是研究…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是個處男  真是多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說你又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有那麼值得自滿的豐富的約會經驗嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不是鑽進學習和研究之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種經驗不是零嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是經歷了一個孤零零的青春時代嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦  處女不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次約會最重要的是要如何給對方留下好印象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於服裝  不需要穿名牌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓人覺得乾淨整潔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有比白大褂更乾淨的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人穿白大褂出去約會的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於約會場所也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要勉強去高檔飯店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去自己平常去的店子就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  誰願意在這種煞風景的店裡約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說其他平常去的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,May  Queen？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次約會去女僕咖啡廳？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器屋本鋪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買武器做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是在對著約會手冊照本宣科而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別一副高高在上的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這美式處女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是美式處女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除你之外還有誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  處男  乙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說  比起看那種書還是這個好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是黃色遊戲的攻略本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起約會不就是色情活動嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牽手什麼的不也很色嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相挽著手然後胸部碰著手臂之類的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太色情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  約會結束時就是接吻結尾吧  可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生贏家們都是混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果  什麼計劃都沒有就早上了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嘟囔了  趕緊換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,標籤撕掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那領帶怎麼打的啊  真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  讓人操心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有種讓人把脖子勒住的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  手帕也帶上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道該怎麼用吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「現在我也在等著你」的暗號？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:34.23,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}「幸福的黃色手帕」是70年代的日本電影，劇中黃色手帕被作為依然在等待的暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是幸福的黃色手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種扭曲的知識算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說太老套了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也知道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「當女生要坐在公園凳子上的時候為她鋪上」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我後面悄悄跟上你們然後在關鍵時刻我會發簡訊給你建議的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你要跟過來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橋田也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:11:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,325)\fscy80\fscx80\fsp0}Operation  Valkyria
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:11:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神作戰  行動開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是北歐神話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在碰頭的時候嚴禁遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最遲也要提前15分鐘到達
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為已經出來得很早了  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我也是剛剛才到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那麼出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是頭一次看到沒穿白大褂的岡部師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  因為是約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和女孩子一起散步的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.43,0:12:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己要自然地走在靠車道的一側
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:12:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不自然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  在與汽車和摩托車擦身而過的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要若無其事地保護女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部師傅？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來只是摔倒了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還在那裡被女僕給救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連餐巾紙都收下了  究竟在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧瀨氏好像很不爽啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今…今天真是風和日麗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是稍微有幾片雲彩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個蛋糕非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  咖啡也很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:14:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  明明至今為止都能很自然地交談
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一想到這是約會就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡真是一家很棒的店啊  經常來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去很不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是對話的傳接球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其…其實今天是第一次來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到第一次的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.68,0:14:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天8月14日是日本史上第一次授予專利的專利紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟在往哪傳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部師傅懂的真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧瀨氏  差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是在看著  什麼忙都沒幫上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我們要看到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很無聊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我這樣的人一起約會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋  你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:14:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要在街上閒逛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小琉佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一個勁地走  都到上野走了一個來回了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得我們初次相遇時候的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被拿著相機的男人們糾纏著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很為難的時候  你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非…非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？為什麼要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我…雖然長成這樣但卻是男的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你是男是女  都沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情怎樣都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候岡部師傅對我說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我感到非常的開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有了那句話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會喜歡上岡部師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那種事情怎樣都無所謂」嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那豈不是琉佳子還是男人的時候的記憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我…我究竟在說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和菲伊莉斯的時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的世界線的記憶…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的是非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成為我的戀人  非常的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的…幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是媽媽的呼叫器號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉肉蔬菜蔬菜肉肉蔬菜蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到這個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漆原小姐的媽媽應該會認為之前的訊息只是惡作劇了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘟嘟嚕  聽我說  聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由氏剛才看到了小琉佳和誰在約會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是小岡倫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？騙人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的絕對不是小岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為穿著普通的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也很有紳士風度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此  那樣的才不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣子琉佳子根本算不上是和我約會過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？但是岡部師傅…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是凶真  連我的名字都忘了嗎  琉佳子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男的  是女的  還是戀人  混亂的其實是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情怎樣都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是我  琉佳子是琉佳子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的話  就把妖刀五月雨拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了琉佳子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來圍繞著這把妖刀的傳說要追溯到義經的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是顯現著死之色的滿月之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤身一人迷了路的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又開始了啊  小岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  和小琉佳和好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:19:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已經不需要我們幫忙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請去救真由理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部師傅正在尋找的古董電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IBN5100嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實到去年的正月為止都在我家的倉庫裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我把它弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在打掃倉庫的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部師傅  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請一定要救真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能久違地和岡部師傅一起修行真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉佳…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話…我會哭出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候就要說慣例的暗號呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EL  PSY  CONGARI
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是CONGROO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EL  PSY…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我並不想變回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  因為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是變回男孩子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不得不把對岡部師傅的這份感情埋藏於心底
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為覺得明明是男的卻還喜歡岡部師傅的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉佳子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變回男孩子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事情也全都會忘記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違的兩人修行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.45,0:20:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣感受著岡部師傅身體的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.19,0:20:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要體會這麼痛苦的心情的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不該許願要成為女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你變回了男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於我來說琉佳子就是琉佳子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有任何改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男是女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情怎樣都無所謂  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  再一會兒就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請記住我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住身為女孩子的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我絕不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚嗚  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  岡部師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漆原琉佳  言行舉止都只能讓人聯想到女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.15,0:21:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是比女孩子更像女孩子的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  琉佳子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突…突然說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.09,0:21:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很敬佩您
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…是男的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的簡訊  還有一條


